## 12. Definition of Done

The work item is done when **all** of these are true:

- [ ] All phases in [`phases/`](./phases/) complete with passing tests.
- [ ] Acceptance criteria from §6 verified.
- [ ] No unresolved Blocker / Major findings in `reviews/`.
- [ ] Security considerations from §8 addressed in code (not deferred).
- [ ] Observability from §9 in place.
- [ ] Rollout from §10 executed; success metric green for stated window.
- [ ] Docs updated where behavior/interfaces changed.
- [ ] Follow-ups filed for anything intentionally deferred.
- [ ] `progress.md` status set to `done`.
